article_title: Trade Names: Kinsale Insurance handles the hardest cases
article_text:
What is it?: Specialty insurance company that is a subsidiary of holding company Kinsale Capital Group Inc.

Location: 2221 Edward Holland Drive in Henrico County

Employees: 109 full time and five part time, including the management team

Owners: Kinsale Capital Group Inc., which is owned by Moelis Capital Partners, Virginia Capital Partners and the company’s senior management team, which includes Michael Kehoe and Bob Neal

Contact: (804) 289-1300 or www.kinsaleins.com

og.description: Kinsale writes commercial insurance policies for businesses that are deemed too risky by standard insurance companies.
